data.description: Beautiful ranch home on the edge of Guilford/Randolph County! Come home every day to this 2-bedroom charming house with a bonus room for guests or as a third bedroom. Drink your morning coffee in the sunroom with amazing natural light with large windows. Huge backyard with a ton of potential for BBQs and parties. Almost completely  fenced in. With a few modern updates, this could be your forever home! Schedule your private showing today! New Dryer, dishwasher, water heater, plumbing, PVC pipes, and new HVAC. Fresh paint throughout and new flooring in bathroom.
